ng above the stage showing photos of coaches and athletes who were killed over the past two years.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A screen\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1357}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1378}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1393}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1397, \"to\": 1404}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1417}, {\"ngram\": \"the past two years\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was dubbed \\\"heaven's team.\\\"\", \"from\": 1459, \"to\": 1489, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"heaven's team\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1487}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ukrainian acting sports minister Matvii Bidnyi thanked Hidalgo for the support France has provided to Ukrainian athletes.\", \"from\": 1491, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1491, \"end\": 1500, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.9724841251396992, \"rank\": 0.028259090082669185, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\"}, {\"begin\": 1546, \"end\": 1553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"score\": 0.9999999967451458, \"rank\": 3.2547700341604267e-09, \"text\": \"Hidalgo\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Miguel_Hidalgo_y_Costilla\"}, {\"begin\": 1570, \"end\": 1576, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.7175146706097957, \"rank\": 0.3737600316834013, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 1593, \"end\": 1602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukraine\", \"score\": 0.972484125139